endance satisfactory evaluation by field placement supervisor weekly reflection papers of three to five pages and a final reflection paper of no less than 15 pages number of units 12 course number 473 all externship courses externship companion seminar externship civil externship criminal externship special circumstances related links axess coursework digital reserve sls registrar rain 57 f 2012 stanford university system requirements help virtual tour
